GoldMiner NFT - Game Rules (service agreement)<br>
GoldMiner NFT Game Rules<br>
•Members rent GoldMiner NFTs at US$ 21, U$S 2.400 or U$S 27.000 (Shovel, Land, Excavator).<br>
•Each Member can rent as many GoldMiner NFTs as they wish.<br>
-Each GoldMiner NFT rental is a 6 months contract.<br>
•Each GoldMiner NFT generates physical gold for the player, which is acquired at an agreed discount price on market. The quantity of gold acquired at the rental date price is registered in the player’s ownership certificate and can be claimed after a 6 months period.<br>
•Members can use FT on their Rewards Cube every 1st and 15th of each month or Deposit Wallet at any time to rent GoldMiner NFTs.<br>
•Members need to deposit Family Token (FT) in the integrated wallet at www.cryptofamilylove.co to be able to rent GoldMiner NFTs.<br>


With GoldMiningNFTs you accumulate gold, that you can claim after 6 months. <br>
 
After 6 months you can: <br>
1. Claim your physical gold <br>
2. Have it delivered to your door (taxes apply) <br>
3. Keep your certificate of ownership with the gold stored in our storage facilities. <br>


